Description:
  Generates a new JSON Schema file for signle action.

  See http://json-schema.org/ for JSON Schema syntax.

Example:

  rails generate schema posts::create title body:required published:boolean:required

  This will create:
    app/schemas/posts/create.yml
      (with title, body and published properties)

  Valid types are:
    - array
    - boolean
    - integer
    - number
    - null
    - object
    - string (default)

